## Summary
This is a sophisticated time tracking application with automatic system event detection, lap-based time segmentation, persistent state management, and a modern responsive UI. Future development focuses on reporting features (weekly/monthly analysis) which will require database integration. Always prioritize accuracy of time tracking and respect user's manual pause intentions.

